1
00:01:08,040 --> 00:01:10,000
[Episode 22: What You Think Matters]

2
00:01:10,840 --> 00:01:13,319
How many more times will you watch it?

3
00:01:13,319 --> 00:01:14,599
Missy,

4
00:01:14,599 --> 00:01:17,000
I'm here to meet my mom's divorce lawyer,

5
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:19,446
not to admire your diamond ring, okay?

6
00:01:20,079 --> 00:01:22,280
But it's really sparkly.

7
00:01:22,280 --> 00:01:24,120
You said it was urgent.

8
00:01:24,120 --> 00:01:26,147
So I stood up the lawyer and came here.

9
00:01:26,147 --> 00:01:27,159
It took me a fortnight

10
00:01:27,159 --> 00:01:29,480
to make an arrangement with him.

11
00:01:29,480 --> 00:01:31,600
Was it just to hear this from you?

12
00:01:31,600 --> 00:01:33,159
I helped you too.

13
00:01:33,159 --> 00:01:36,045
That's why I came. I thought...

14
00:01:37,760 --> 00:01:38,982
Never mind.

15
00:01:40,799 --> 00:01:42,241
Thought what?

16
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:44,645
I'm forced to marry?

17
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:51,063
I tried on wedding dresses a few days ago.

18
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:53,198
How did you feel?

19
00:01:57,520 --> 00:02:00,045
It cinches in at the waist
to make you look slim.

20
00:02:03,110 --> 00:02:04,640
Okay, Mrs. Lu.

21
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:05,960
Honey,

22
00:02:05,960 --> 00:02:07,100
turn around.

23
00:02:10,360 --> 00:02:11,440
Good dog.

24
00:02:12,039 --> 00:02:13,483
Finished, Mr. Lu.

25
00:02:15,160 --> 00:02:16,262
Not bad.

26
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:19,640
Don't eat this.

27
00:02:19,640 --> 00:02:21,634
Who are you video chatting with?

28
00:02:24,360 --> 00:02:25,517
My dog.

29
00:02:34,680 --> 00:02:35,934
Show me the rear.

30
00:03:02,719 --> 00:03:04,080
What's on your mind?

31
00:03:04,080 --> 00:03:05,640
Why the silence?

32
00:03:05,640 --> 00:03:07,407
I felt...

33
00:03:09,755 --> 00:03:11,320
good.

34
00:03:11,320 --> 00:03:12,595
Really?

35
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:15,240
If it's good,

36
00:03:15,240 --> 00:03:17,797
why do you need my approval?

37
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:31,640
Why wasn't I cast in <i>First Love</i>?

38
00:03:31,640 --> 00:03:33,337
You said I've improved!

39
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:38,225
So you knew it all along?

40
00:03:43,440 --> 00:03:44,960
Tell me why.

41
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:46,360
Do you know Fang Fang?

42
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:47,800
An emerging actor.

43
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:49,563
He wants the role.

44
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:52,759
A superstar plays a supporting role?

45
00:03:52,759 --> 00:03:55,072
His agent told the casting crew

46
00:03:55,072 --> 00:03:56,680
that no remuneration

47
00:03:56,680 --> 00:03:58,400
or billing order is required.

48
00:03:58,400 --> 00:04:00,060
Did you support me?

49
00:04:01,039 --> 00:04:02,200
It's my project.

50
00:04:02,200 --> 00:04:05,039
I don't want them to think you swing it.

51
00:04:05,039 --> 00:04:06,039
So what?

52
00:04:06,039 --> 00:04:08,439
I want the role, the role!

53
00:04:08,439 --> 00:04:10,800
It's based on popularity and buzz.

54
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:12,648
At least help me!

55
00:04:12,648 --> 00:04:15,280
Hey, isn't the pal you?

56
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:17,480
Isn't the ex Ren Xi Zhou?

57
00:04:17,480 --> 00:04:19,160
You two dated secretly

58
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:21,360
and treated others as pawns.

59
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:22,720
I lent you items and assisted you.

60
00:04:22,720 --> 00:04:24,199
Wasn't I good enough to you?

61
00:04:24,199 --> 00:04:26,280
After all, I once...

62
00:04:26,280 --> 00:04:27,880
I wanted to go public.

63
00:04:27,880 --> 00:04:30,200
But she thought it wasn't stable

64
00:04:30,200 --> 00:04:31,639
and didn't want others to know.

65
00:04:31,639 --> 00:04:33,240
Or we'd be awkward if we broke up.

66
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:35,461
Is that the concern?

67
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:41,800
You helped me.

68
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:43,578
It's my fault for not getting you the role.

69
00:04:43,578 --> 00:04:44,639
I apologize.

70
00:04:44,639 --> 00:04:45,759
No, that's not right!

71
00:04:45,759 --> 00:04:47,480
I helped you not because of the role,

72
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:49,560
but because I wanted to help you as a friend.

73
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:52,298
So I thought you'd also
do me a favor as a friend.

74
00:04:52,298 --> 00:04:53,760
I'm not only your friend,

75
00:04:53,760 --> 00:04:55,679
but also the scriptwriter.

76
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:02,495
Maybe next time.

77
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:05,759
You're talented. You became famous at 28.

78
00:05:05,759 --> 00:05:07,240
You have so many opportunities.

79
00:05:07,240 --> 00:05:09,406
But I'm not. I don't.

80
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:11,160
Next time?

81
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:12,600
Which time?

82
00:05:12,600 --> 00:05:13,839
If there's a chance next time,

83
00:05:13,839 --> 00:05:15,558
and the investor wants me...

84
00:05:18,280 --> 00:05:19,723
I'll think about it.

85
00:05:30,479 --> 00:05:32,360
I suggest you refuse.

86
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:33,560
Why?

87
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:37,000
If you need others' approval to do something,

88
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:38,820
you'd better refuse it.

89
00:05:38,820 --> 00:05:43,320
I think it's pre-wedding anxiety.

90
00:05:43,320 --> 00:05:45,399
I just want your comfort.

91
00:05:45,399 --> 00:05:47,600
I'm not here to comfort you.

92
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:50,240
I want you to make the right decision.

93
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:52,527
Thanks to your return with your dad,

94
00:05:52,527 --> 00:05:56,279
my mom and I could handle the crap back home.

95
00:05:56,279 --> 00:05:58,120
I'm grateful to you.

96
00:05:58,120 --> 00:05:59,680
But if it means

97
00:05:59,680 --> 00:06:03,240
sacrificing my friend's marital freedom,

98
00:06:03,240 --> 00:06:05,160
then I don't want it.

99
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:06,520
Understand?

100
00:06:07,639 --> 00:06:09,466
What's the right decision?

101
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:11,920
You don't have to be a heroine.

102
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:14,879
As a friend, I want you to be happy.

103
00:06:14,879 --> 00:06:16,639
If you don't want marriage,

104
00:06:16,639 --> 00:06:18,240
you can refuse.

105
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:20,280
It's the right decision for you,

106
00:06:20,280 --> 00:06:22,139
not me!

107
00:06:25,327 --> 00:06:26,560
You know what?

108
00:06:26,560 --> 00:06:28,600
Among a shoal of serranidae,

109
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:30,759
usually one to three males

110
00:06:30,759 --> 00:06:32,720
swim around a female.

111
00:06:32,720 --> 00:06:36,280
It gives the females a sense of security,

112
00:06:36,280 --> 00:06:39,026
and is conducive to foraging.

113
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:41,360
I'm not like you.

114
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:43,816
A black-crowned night heron can fly in the sky,

115
00:06:44,400 --> 00:06:45,800
but serranidae...

116
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:49,203
I can only swim around my dad.

117
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:51,600
Xi Zhou,

118
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:52,720
if I don't get married,

119
00:06:52,720 --> 00:06:54,320
my dad would neglect me,

120
00:06:54,320 --> 00:06:55,560
as if I weren't his daughter.

121
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:57,560
Yet I can't survive alone.

122
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:59,480
All I can do is paint.

123
00:06:59,480 --> 00:07:01,319
But if my paintings don't sell,

124
00:07:01,319 --> 00:07:03,480
I have to crash a meal at my friend's place.

125
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:05,639
I don't want to live this way.

126
00:07:05,639 --> 00:07:07,920
I fear hardship, poverty,

127
00:07:07,920 --> 00:07:10,305
even more than the loss of freedom!

128
00:07:13,200 --> 00:07:15,389
More than the loss of dignity,

129
00:07:16,000 --> 00:07:17,395
happiness,

130
00:07:17,959 --> 00:07:19,456
and everything?

131
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:23,600
Money is everything.

132
00:07:23,600 --> 00:07:26,079
But that's not what you want.

133
00:07:26,079 --> 00:07:28,200
That's the way I am!

134
00:07:28,200 --> 00:07:30,439
You can sit here and persuade me,

135
00:07:30,439 --> 00:07:33,360
because you don't have it in your life.

136
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:34,920
If you had it,

137
00:07:34,920 --> 00:07:37,320
you'd struggle and suffer like I do,

138
00:07:37,320 --> 00:07:40,260
and try your best to get it, wouldn't you?

139
00:07:52,320 --> 00:07:53,686
Xi Zhou,

140
00:07:54,720 --> 00:07:56,519
I've made my choice.

141
00:07:57,440 --> 00:07:59,439
Say something.

142
00:07:59,439 --> 00:08:01,602
Did I make the right choice?

143
00:08:02,640 --> 00:08:04,105
You're right.

144
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:05,972
I'm not you.

145
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:09,484
Perhaps it's the wrong choice for me,

146
00:08:10,079 --> 00:08:12,077
but not necessarily for you.

147
00:08:13,416 --> 00:08:15,200
We're different.

148
00:08:15,200 --> 00:08:17,319
But whatever you choose,

149
00:08:17,319 --> 00:08:19,654
as long as you're happy, it's good.

150
00:08:22,480 --> 00:08:23,988
Are you happy?

151
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:27,990
I wish you happiness.

152
00:08:33,720 --> 00:08:36,954
Maybe I should change my career.

153
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:50,156
Hello?

154
00:08:51,480 --> 00:08:53,159
Harbor crew?

155
00:08:53,159 --> 00:08:55,212
Yes, yes, yes. I'm available.

156
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:57,600
Add me on WeChat.

157
00:08:57,600 --> 00:08:58,965
By this number.

158
00:09:07,840 --> 00:09:10,423
Hello, sir. I'm Zhu Qiao Fei.

159
00:09:11,679 --> 00:09:12,840
<i>Audition address:</i>

160
00:09:12,840 --> 00:09:14,080
<i>Guangcheng Crown Hotel.</i>

161
00:09:14,080 --> 00:09:15,440
<i>Time: 16:00, September 1st.</i>

162
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:16,695
Okay.

163
00:09:17,879 --> 00:09:19,120
<i>We haven't checked in yet.</i>

164
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:20,799
<i>I'll tell you the room number later.</i>

165
00:09:20,799 --> 00:09:23,159
The room number for an audition?

166
00:09:23,159 --> 00:09:24,637
What does that mean?

167
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:32,525
Is she going to...

168
00:09:33,519 --> 00:09:34,642
No, no.

169
00:09:37,120 --> 00:09:39,140
Thank you for your appreciation.

170
00:09:39,140 --> 00:09:40,776
Maybe next time...

171
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:47,760
[Lu Shang &amp; Li Nan Xi]
Li Nan Xi's wedding?

172
00:09:47,760 --> 00:09:50,425
At Guangcheng Crown Hotel?

173
00:09:50,425 --> 00:09:51,440
Hello?

174
00:09:51,440 --> 00:09:52,559
<i>I'm getting married.</i>

175
00:09:52,559 --> 00:09:53,600
With whom?

176
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:55,080
That's so sudden.

177
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:56,759
<i>A tall, rich, and handsome guy.</i>

178
00:09:56,759 --> 00:09:57,759
<i>Will you come?</i>

179
00:09:57,759 --> 00:09:59,360
<i>If you will, I'll cover it.</i>

180
00:09:59,360 --> 00:10:00,880
Wow.

181
00:10:00,880 --> 00:10:03,339
<i>Does "wow" mean yes or an exclamation?</i>

182
00:10:03,960 --> 00:10:07,160
<i>If I go, I'll audition too.</i>

183
00:10:07,160 --> 00:10:09,789
<i>It's said to be an audition, but maybe...</i>

184
00:10:12,840 --> 00:10:14,160
<i>Next time.</i>

185
00:10:14,160 --> 00:10:15,320
<i>Which time?</i>

186
00:10:15,320 --> 00:10:16,600
<i>If there's a chance next time,</i>

187
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:18,097
<i>and the investor wants me...</i>

188
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:20,397
<i>I'll still...</i>

189
00:10:21,400 --> 00:10:23,933
[Wedding of Li Nan Xi and Lu Shang]

190
00:10:29,960 --> 00:10:31,280
Take it.

191
00:10:31,280 --> 00:10:33,006
Just your former company.

192
00:10:34,360 --> 00:10:36,400
You'll have a court hearing in Nanwan that day.

193
00:10:36,400 --> 00:10:38,040
And we're looking for another lawyer.

194
00:10:38,040 --> 00:10:39,640
I don't have the mood.

195
00:10:41,879 --> 00:10:43,490
You quarreled?

196
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:45,869
Not really.

197
00:10:47,960 --> 00:10:49,457
Is it obvious?

198
00:10:52,120 --> 00:10:54,600
A mother knows her daughter best.

199
00:10:54,600 --> 00:10:56,320
A classical Chinese quotation?

200
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:57,853
From a TV series

201
00:10:58,919 --> 00:11:01,120
written by your friend.

202
00:11:01,120 --> 00:11:02,453
It's quite good.

203
00:11:03,080 --> 00:11:05,064
He is a famous scriptwriter.

204
00:11:09,320 --> 00:11:10,552
[I'll be in the firm at 15:00 this afternoon.]

205
00:11:10,552 --> 00:11:12,197
[If you're available,
we can discuss with the defendant.]

206
00:11:13,240 --> 00:11:14,520
I got it, Lawyer Zhou.

207
00:11:14,520 --> 00:11:16,076
I'll be right there.

208
00:11:16,879 --> 00:11:17,913
Mom.

209
00:11:19,120 --> 00:11:22,280
The divorce is between him and me.

210
00:11:22,280 --> 00:11:23,960
Please don't interfere.

211
00:11:23,960 --> 00:11:26,699
Besides, I'd better handle it myself.

212
00:11:27,519 --> 00:11:28,730
Don't worry.

213
00:11:29,399 --> 00:11:31,480
Got it, Ms. Ren.

214
00:11:31,480 --> 00:11:34,879
But this time, if you can't handle it,

215
00:11:34,879 --> 00:11:36,799
you must, absolutely,

216
00:11:36,799 --> 00:11:38,440
tell me.

217
00:11:38,440 --> 00:11:39,653
Okay?

218
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:42,035
Okay!

219
00:11:45,120 --> 00:11:47,480
You needn't attend the trial hearing.

220
00:11:47,480 --> 00:11:50,600
A friend's wedding is once-in-a-lifetime.

221
00:11:50,600 --> 00:11:52,400
Didn't you quarrel?

222
00:11:52,400 --> 00:11:54,120
She gave you an invitation

223
00:11:54,120 --> 00:11:56,280
and a way out.

224
00:11:56,280 --> 00:11:57,840
I know.

225
00:11:57,840 --> 00:12:00,639
And it's bilateral.

226
00:12:00,639 --> 00:12:02,535
- You and Nan Feng...
- We don't!

227
00:12:05,400 --> 00:12:06,976
Obvious too?

228
00:12:09,440 --> 00:12:11,599
You're so stubborn.

229
00:12:23,600 --> 00:12:25,480
Quarreled with Qiao Fei?

230
00:12:25,480 --> 00:12:26,720
You knew it?

231
00:12:26,720 --> 00:12:28,372
He's absent for so long.

232
00:12:35,120 --> 00:12:36,960
Vexed with the wedding?

233
00:12:36,960 --> 00:12:38,080
Let's flip a coin.

234
00:12:38,080 --> 00:12:39,153
Heads, you go.

235
00:12:39,760 --> 00:12:41,055
Tails, you don't.

236
00:12:49,960 --> 00:12:51,440
Which side?

237
00:12:51,440 --> 00:12:53,080
It doesn't matter.

238
00:12:53,080 --> 00:12:55,360
What matters is your thought

239
00:12:55,360 --> 00:12:57,040
when checking it.

240
00:13:46,000 --> 00:13:48,624
Why not somewhere else?

241
00:13:54,680 --> 00:13:56,912
With my former setup.

242
00:14:11,912 --> 00:14:13,008
Improperly folded.

243
00:14:13,008 --> 00:14:14,279
Go and play there.

244
00:14:14,279 --> 00:14:15,820
Chipped bowl.

245
00:14:27,120 --> 00:14:28,920
<i>Li Nan Xi.</i>

246
00:14:28,920 --> 00:14:31,010
<i>Is it on purpose or by accident?</i>

247
00:14:34,080 --> 00:14:35,965
<i>So awkward.</i>

248
00:14:37,040 --> 00:14:40,077
<i>Should he speak first or should I?</i>
